# ☁️ AWS EC2 Hands-On Project

## 📌 Overview

This project focuses on Amazon EC2 (Elastic Compute Cloud), a core AWS service used to launch and manage virtual servers in the cloud.

The project covers launching EC2 instances, configuring security settings, connecting using SSH, and understanding different EC2 instance types and pricing models.

---

# 🚀 Services Used

* Amazon EC2
* AWS IAM
* Security Groups
* Key Pairs
* AWS Management Console

---

# 🖥️ What is EC2?

Amazon EC2 (Elastic Compute Cloud) provides secure and resizable compute capacity in the cloud.

It allows users to:

* Launch virtual servers
* Scale infrastructure on demand
* Deploy applications globally
* Manage compute resources efficiently

